text: Coenocharopa elegans, the elegant pinwheel snail, is a species of air- breathing land snails in the family Charopidae. It is found in Queensland, Australia. == References == == External links == * Coenocharopa elegans at Biolib.cz * Coenocharopa elegans at the Atlas of Living Australia Category:Charopidae Category:Gastropods described in 2010 Category:Fauna of Queensland Category:Gastropods of Australia
